14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 2, Chapter 343, O.S.L.
16 2023 (19 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 215.41), is amended to read as
17 follows:
18 Section 215.41. Subject to availability of funding, there is
19 established until October 1, 2025, within the District Attorneys
20 Council under the direction of the Executive Coordinator of the
21 District Attorneys Council, the position of Sexual Assault Nurse
22 Examiner (SANE) Statewide Coordinator. The Statewide Coordinator
23 shall oversee forensic medical examination training throughout the
24 state, recruit and develop SANE professionals, create and expand
